title: Strengthenings of theorems of the main part
content: Typically, these are biconditional versions of theorems in the main part which are formulated as implications. They could be added after said implication, or sometimes replace it (by "inlining" it). This section contained ~ sb3b , now moved to Main. This could also be done for ~ hba1 , ~ hbe1 , ~ hbe1a , ~ hbn1 , ~ modal5 .
